  ["t-user-1", "user", "global", "approved", "Project owner: Li",
   "mail@ligoldragon.com. Mentci creator. Prefers jj-centric workflow, Rust-only policy, datalog-native design.",
   "2026-03-16", "2026-03-16", "manifest", "proven"],
  ["t-project-1", "project", "global", "approved", "Mentci v1 is successor to Mentci-AI (now Mentci-v0)",
   "Original at criome/Mentci renamed to criome/Mentci-v0. New project at LiGoldragon/Mentci. Two-agent architecture: Samskara (pure datalog) + Lojix (DSL transpiler).",
